<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Drought Information System Mapping</title>

    <style>
        *{
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
            box-sizing:border-box;
        }

        body{
            background:#fafafa;
            font-family: Georgia, serif;
            color:#0b0400;
        }

        /* NAVBAR */
        nav{
            height:50px;
            background:linear-gradient(to right,#1e1208,#7b4a2b);
            display:flex;
            justify-content:flex-end;
            align-items:center;
            padding-right:40px;
        }

        nav span{
            color:white;
            font-size:24px;
            font-weight:bold;
        }

        /* BODY */
        .container{
            text-align:center;
            max-width:1300px;
            margin: 120px auto;
            padding:20px;
        }

        h1{
            font-size:50px;
            margin-bottom:30px;
        }

        h3{
            font-size:30px;
            margin-bottom:6px;
        }

        p{
            font-size:18px;
            line-height:1.7;
            margin-bottom:20px;
        }

        /* BUTTON */
        .buttons{
            margin-top:80px;
            display:flex;
            justify-content:center;
            gap:20px;
        }

        .btn{
            text-decoration:none;
            color:white;
            background:linear-gradient(to right,#c97f57,#1e1208);
            padding:25px 40px;
            border-radius:15px;
            font-size:24px;
            font-weight:bold;
            min-width:200px;
            transition:0.3s;
        }

        .btn:hover{
            transform:translateY(-3px);
            opacity:0.9;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <nav>
        <span>Home</span>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">

        <h1>Drought Information System Mapping</h1>

        <h3>Welcome to the Drought Information System Mapping website.</h3>

        <p>
            Platform ini menyediakan informasi komprehensif terkait kekeringan
            di wilayah Kabupaten Gunungkidul
            Mulai dari visualisasi kekeringan per wilayahnya serta informasi
            terkait dengan bagaimana tingkat kekeringan itu sendiri.
        </p>

        <div class="buttons">
            <a href="about.html" class="btn">About</a>
            <a href="map.html" class="btn">Map</a>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
